trans-unit.source: Provides data for a PropertyChanged event, which you must create.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para um evento PropertyChanged, que você deve criar.

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION]> Classes dentro de <xref:System.Printing>namespace não têm suporte para uso dentro de um serviço do Windows ou serviço ou aplicativo ASP.NET.</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: Tentativa de usar essas classes de dentro de um desses tipos de aplicativo pode gerar problemas inesperados, como diminuído exceções de desempenho e tempo de execução de serviço.

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Se você quiser imprimir a partir de um aplicativo Windows Forms, consulte o <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>namespace.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The name of the property that changed.
trans-unit.target: O nome da propriedade que foram alteradas.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos usados pelo <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar Dispose quando terminar de usar o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O método Dispose deixa a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>em um estado inutilizável.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar Dispose, você deve liberar todas as referências para o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>para que o coletor de lixo possa recuperar a memória que o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>estava ocupando.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método Dispose](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada Dispose antes de liberar sua última referência a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using are not freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> object.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está usando não são liberados até o coletor de lixo chama o <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>método de <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>objeto.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos não gerenciados usados pelo <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"> </xref> e, opcionalmente, libera os recursos gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Este método é chamado pelo <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>método.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the unnamed Boolean parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`invoca o protegido `Dispose(Boolean)` método com o parâmetro booliano sem nome definido como `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with the parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>invoca `Dispose` com o parâmetro definido `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the Boolean parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> references.
trans-unit.target: Quando o parâmetro booliano é `true`, esse método libera todos os recursos mantidos por qualquer objeto gerenciado que este <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>referências.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Este método chama o `Dispose()` método de cada objeto referenciado.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>para liberar recursos gerenciados e não gerenciados; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> para liberar apenas recursos não gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the property that changed.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome da propriedade que foram alteradas.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that holds the property name.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.String>que contém o nome da propriedade.</xref:System.String>
